Orange Bowl BoysChapter #36: Your HonorablenessShow Notes8 DAYS UNTIL CANES KICKOFF!!!! The Boys gave us their final off-season episode as they went through the roster one last time and picked every game on the schedule. We had predictions of 10-2, 9-3 and 8-4 for the season and things got a little heated on a few games. Someone has us losing at home to FSU…WHAT!?! We did some 5 Questions for the last time and even talked about the new stadium renderings that dropped this week.
